        public DefaultPrefixConfig(Collection<String> prefixesCollection,
                   String prefixString)
        Instantiates a new prefix store. Using the given prefixesCollection as known prefixes. The given prefix will be used as defaultPrefix and has to be part of the given prefixesCollection
        Parameters:
        prefixesCollection - the prefixes collection to be used as known prefixes
        prefixString - the default prefix string
